Package org.grobid.core.data

Class Summary
Affiliation Class for representing and exchanging affiliation information.
BibDataSet Structure for representing the different information for a citation and its different context of citation.
BiblioItem Class for representing and exchanging a bibliographical item.
BiblioSet Class for representing authority lists for bibliographies.
ChemicalEntity Class for managing chemical entities.
Classification Class for representing a classification.
Date Class for representing a date.
Passage Class for managing passage of citations.
PatentItem Class for managing patent bibliographical references.
Person Class for representing and exchanging person information, e.g. author or editor.
PriorArtCitation Class for managing citation of patent bibliographical references.
